# VHS demo tape — search_code trace
Output demo-trace.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 950
Set Height 600
Set Padding 12
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Type "cd ~/my-rails-app"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "rails 'ai:tool[search_code]' pattern=publishable match_type=trace"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 3s
